<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd">
<t:content>
	<div style="border: 20px solid #f5f5dc;">
		<div>
			<div>
				<strong><em>OrderList</em></strong> &lt;&lt;total:
				&nbsp;${orders.total} items
			</div>

			<div class="order-list">
				<t:loop source="orders.returns" value="order">
					<div class="order-block">
						<div class="order-header">
							<span>订单号: ${order.id}</span> <span class="spliter">|</span> <span>时间:${order.gmtCreate}</span>
							<span class="spliter">|</span> <span class="buyer">${order.buyerMemberId }</span>
						</div>
						<div class="sub-header" style="border-bottom: solid 1px red;">
							<div class="left">
								<div>买家备注: 发顺风寄付；</div>
								<div>卖家备注: 无货不发；这是测试；；</div>
							</div>
							<div class="right">
								<div class="status">等待买家付款</div>
								<div class="spliter right"></div>
								<div class="money right">共计8件，${order.sumPaymentDouble}元(运费：${order.carriageDouble}元)</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
						<div class="address">${order.toFullName},${order.toMobile},
							${order.toArea} (${order.toPost})</div>
						<div class="clear"></div>

						<div class="details">
							<table>
								<t:loop source="order.orderEntities" value="entity"
									index="index">
									<tr>
										<td>${index}</td>
										<td>${entity.productName}</td>
										<td><t:loop source="entity.specInfo?.keySet()"
												value="specName">
												${specName}:${specValue}<br />
											</t:loop></td>
										<td>${entity.price}</td>
										<td>${entity.quantity}</td>
									</tr>
								</t:loop>
								<tr>
									<td>2</td>
									<td>2013春装新款显瘦女装呛口小辣椒KAKI秀重工奢华宝石徽章钉珠毛衣</td>
								</tr>
							</table>
						</div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
					</div>
				</t:loop>
			</div>

		</div>
		<strong><em>order list.... {${orders}}</em></strong>
	</div>
</t:content>
</html>
